There's so much you can do using BigQuery with your Analytics data, but sometimes it's hard to know just how to get started. In this video, Todd Kerpelman explains how your Google Analytics for Firebase data is stored in BigQuery, and then shows you some important tips on working with this data as we create queries to answer your burning analytics questions.

