Firebase just announced the beta release of Cloud Firestore -- a fully-managed NoSQL document database for mobile and web app development. It's designed to easily store and sync app data at global scale, and it's now available in beta. In this video, the product leads -- Jonny Dimond, Sarah Allen, and Alex Dufetel -- share all the details and will demonstrate how to build a scalable app with Cloud Firestore.

